@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hozvsi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((tmp - 0.04))
    tmp = v0
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.74) - (tmp + 0.28 * v1 + 0.90)) / wp.exp((v1 + 0.54 + v2 + 0.05)))
    v1 = v1
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.04)))
    data[tid] = v0
